Package: c2z
Type: Package
Title: A Reference Manager in R
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2023-03-11
Authors@R: person("Øystein Olav","Skaar", role=c("aut","cre","cph"),
    email="oeysan@gmail.com",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5605-3492"))
Maintainer: Øystein Olav Skaar <oeysan@gmail.com>
Description: Cristin to Zotero (c2z) aims at obtaining total dominion 
    over Cristin (Current Research Information SysTem in Norway) and Zotero. 
    The package enables manipulating Zotero libraries using R. Import 
    references from Cristin, regjeringen.no, CRAN, ISBN (Alma, LoC), and DOI 
    (CrossRef, DataCite) to a Zotero library. Add, edit, copy, or delete 
    items, including attacments and collections, and export references to 
    BibLaTeX (and other formats).
